flowchart TD
    A[Incoming Query] --> B{Is it from<br/>semantic layer?}
    
    B -->|Yes| C[Check metric<br/>definition]
    B -->|No| D[Ad-hoc query]
    
    C --> E{Has 'formula'<br/>field?}
    E -->|Yes| F[Route to<br/>DuckDB]
    E -->|No| G{Has 'expression'<br/>field?}
    
    G -->|Yes| H{Single<br/>table?}
    G -->|No| X[❌ Invalid<br/>metric]
    
    H -->|Yes| I[Route to<br/>PyIceberg]
    H -->|No| F
    
    D --> D1{Query type?}
    D1 -->|Schema query| J[Metadata<br/>API]
    D1 -->|Simple filter| I
    D1 -->|JOIN required| K{enable_sql<br/>= true?}
    
    K -->|Yes| F
    K -->|No| L[❌ Error:<br/>JOINs require<br/>DuckDB]
    
    I --> M[✅ Type-safe execution<br/>Zero SQL injection risk<br/>PyIceberg expressions]
    F --> N[✅ Controlled SQL<br/>from semantic layer<br/>DuckDB engine]
    J --> O[✅ Direct catalog access<br/>Schema metadata]
    
    M --> P[Return formatted<br/>results to user]
    N --> P
    O --> P
    
    style A fill:#e1f5ff
    style I fill:#d4edda
    style F fill:#d4edda
    style J fill:#d4edda
    style M fill:#c3e6cb
    style N fill:#c3e6cb
    style O fill:#c3e6cb
    style P fill:#b8daff
    style X fill:#f8d7da
    style L fill:#f8d7da